docs/index.rst
     1Рєњ``pluggy``
     2Рєњ==========
     3Рєњ**The pytest plugin system**
     4Рєњ
     5РєњWhat is it?
     6Рєњ***********
     7Рєњ``pluggy`` is the crystallized core of :ref:`plugin management and hook
     8Рєњcalling <pytest:writing-plugins>` for :std:doc:`pytest <pytest:index>`.
     9РєњIt enables `1400+ plugins`_ to extend and customize ``pytest``'s default
    10Рєњbehaviour. Even ``pytest`` itself is composed as a set of ``pluggy`` plugins
    11Рєњwhich are invoked in sequence according to a well defined set of protocols.
    12Рєњ
    13РєњIt gives users the ability to extend or modify the behaviour of a
      РєњРђд

